title: 10000.BC.Complete
description:
10,000 BC is a UK reality TV series which follows 20 British people from all walks of life as they go back to the conditions of the Stone Age and try to survive two months in the wilderness.

The series was set and filmed in the Byalka Hunting Preserve, near Lovech in the foothills of the Balkan Mountains, Bulgaria. The contestants were filmed for two months from October 2014.

The individual episodes in this file have been compiled from various sources
